No. No. It used to be - do this - do that - do the other, take the - you see the 
- the two sisters - the oldest of them was - four and a half years younger than myself and the other was sixteen and a half - see, and of course the youngest one altogether was - when I was about sixteen when she was born and there was a brother in betwee
n.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9141532 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid656999\charrsid7276462 So there were four - of you were there?
