something he - well, Uncle came over - I'd never seen him before. He came over about 1912 or 13 and took father back with him. Father in the meantime when - on his pension. I don't - I suppose father would have been sixty by then or near abuts. Well, look
 here - I told you the - when he was born - '55. Well now -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9141532 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid656999\charrsid7276462 He would have been around 58 or 59.
