e ordinary suit wore out and got shabby well you; had a new suit for Sundays. And - and, of course with - with regard to the girls - all the same with - with - if - if we'd had two boys near of an age - but - of course - so far as I was concerned - well, 
I
 was practically grown up before the boy was born you see - nine years difference in - well, I was a big boy anyway - I was nine when he was born. So by the time - there's no point in saving any of my left offs for him but with regard the - to the girls, 
