d bits like that. But of course - you know, you can continue to do that if you will. See, it's just like going - like people who win a lot of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7805942\charrsid7276462 money}{\rtlch\fcs1 
