 you another thing that they used to do to - mother and father'd go out and I - well, I couldn't have been much more that about eight or nine - I'd be left in charge of the others. They'd be put to bed and - you know, I used to sit down in the kitchen, I 
u
sed to read a rare lot - well I - I still read quite a bit, and - you know, and I used to - think on this and they won't - you know, I used to be scared stiff they'd take; you know what children are - they have a kind of a nightmare or whatever it is, you
 know, and I'd be scared stiff and I know - I know if have to go up and attend to 'em you know -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9141532 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid656999\charrsid7276462 Did it sometimes happen that they woke?
