 and - something, and they they had what they called a high tea. That was the average family - I'm not talking about our own family - the average family. And the girls'd have their hair crimped up in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10032058\charrsid7276462 curlers}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid656999\charrsid7276462  Go about
