Oh well they - they - they made all sorts of promises and - when - when I - they said when you get }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5466981 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
