s I know. I never saw anything. 'Cos I - I suppose really they spent it in - of course they used to keep us in clothes and boots and shoes and I suppose that's where it went I don't know. I never had it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9141532 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid656999\charrsid7276462 When you say it turned up with string and seali
ng wax on it you mean it came through the post?
