pose they did. Only of course that was when they used to - that didn't used to worry us a lot you know, I mean, if they - yes, I suppose they did. You might -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9141532 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid656999\charrsid7276462 I was wondering who they associated with?
