Oh a little bit you know. I mean, we weren't all that strict. But mind - what we said we meant. Now look here, you can see children and - and parents you go to a - you go to a shop with your children maybe
 and they're pottering round and meddling with things, see. Don't do it. You tell them not to do it but they do it just the same, see. Whereas - we never allowed that sort of thing see, and - and - what we said went, see? If we said no we meant no. See, b
ut of course a lot of people say no and mean yes, you know what I mean - with children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9141532 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid656999\charrsid7276462 Did you and your wife have the same attitudes to bringing up the children?

