Oh yes. Oh yes. Oh yes, we agreed about that. Only - the only - any time - any time
 - we had occasion to disagree - it was never in front of the children, see. See. And if - if they appealed to their mother or - or to me, see, well your mother said so and so - or daddy said so and so, see, it went. But of course when they'd gone to bed 
we might discuss the question. Though we didn't quarrel about it - just -
