 said I do stipulate one thing, I said, that is, if I come back which of course was very doubtful then - if I come back I said I want a place to come to I said and I don't want to go with your parents or me own. See? But of course when I come back there w
as such a shortage. You couldn't get a place. So for the time being we had to much in with them, see. But -
