Well - yes, I should have voted if - if there was a Labour. You see, the servants were separate from the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9261670\charrsid7276462 other people}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid656999\charrsid7276462  and you know some of those - some of those ladies would go to the Army and Navy Stores. They'd buy so much tea and then they'd buy so much servant's tea which was a -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9141532 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid656999\charrsid7276462 A cheaper type?
