bbery that used to be was funny you know. For instance, a lady's maid - would have nothing to do with a parlour maid or a - a - see what I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9141532 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid656999\charrsid7276462 You mean both inside and outside the house?
