\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6448152 WB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid656999\charrsid7276462 Oh yes, you used to hear about that now and again and - you know, if th
e - servant - if the house was away, you know, the - that - from about - well August was absolutely dead in the West End, everybody's on holiday. But if the servants were left they were on what they called board wages. See, they paid them so much for thei
r keep in some cases they - they took the servants or some of the servants with 'em. Buy some of these place they used to have quite a number of people. Oh yes.
